Business Requirement Prioritization:

High Priority: Must-Have requirements.

Medium Priority: Good-to-Have requirements.

Low Priority: Nice-to-Have requirements.

Tech Team Assessment:

Focus on High Priority and Existing items.

Determine if current tools meet these requirements or if improvements are needed.

Key Questions for Tech Team:

Identify the key contact for decision-making.

Confirm who is responsible for decisions and when reviews will take place.

Request a gap analysis to identify any discrepancies.

Coordination with Talent Team:

Share the gap analysis findings with Lara and the Talent team.

Weekly Update Meetings:

Schedule weekly calls to discuss status and action items.

Participants include both the Tech Team and Viva Engagement Team.

Ensure clarity on responsibilities and next steps during these updates.
